# Ghi chu:
# - API_URL dung cho mobile/native va local debug.
# - API_URL_WEB dung rieng cho web:
#   + auto: web tu dong dung same-origin cua trang dang mo
#   + https://api.tenmien.com: web goi toi host nay
# - Khi deploy web production, uu tien de API_URL_WEB=auto va dat reverse proxy cung domain/https.
